<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF8C42 0%, #FF6B35 100%);
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #0F172A;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    }
    .text-block {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #475569;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    }
    .highlight-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF5EB 0%, #FFE8D6 100%);
      border-left: 4px solid #FF8C42;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .highlight-box h2 {
      color: #FF6B35;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    }
    .highlight-box p {
      color: #0F172A;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF8C42 0%, #FF6B35 100%);
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 15px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .footer p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #64748B;
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    }
    ul {
      color: #475569;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    ul li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .application-summary {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .application-summary p {
      margin: 8px 0;
      color: #475569;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .application-summary strong {
      color: #0F172A;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Application Received!</h1>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="content">
      <p class="greeting">Hi <%= @partner_application.name %>!</p>

      <p class="text-block">
        Thank you for your interest in joining the AI Talk Coach Partner Program! We've received your application and are excited to review it.
      </p>

      <!-- Application Summary -->
      <div class="application-summary">
        <p><strong>Your Application Details:</strong></p>
        <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= @partner_application.name %></p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @partner_application.email %></p>
        <p><strong>Partner Type:</strong> <%= @partner_application.partner_type %></p>
        <% if @partner_application.message.present? %>
          <p><strong>Message:</strong> <%= @partner_application.message %></p>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <!-- Highlight Box -->
      <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2>What's Next?</h2>
        <p>
          Our team will review your application within the next 3-5 business days. We'll reach out via email with next steps and information about setting up your partner account.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-block">
        <strong>While You Wait:</strong>
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Learn more about our platform at <%= @partners_url %></li>
        <li>Think about how you'd like to integrate AI Talk Coach with your audience</li>
        <li>Prepare any questions you have about the program</li>
        <li>Consider what promotional materials would work best for your community</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-block">
        We're building something special togetherâ€”a platform that helps people genuinely improve their communication skills. As a partner, you'll be helping your audience unlock their full potential while earning a sustainable income.
      </p>

      <center>
        <a href="<%= @partners_url %>" class="cta-button">Learn More About the Program</a>
      </center>

      <p class="text-block" style="margin-top: 30px;">
        If you have any questions in the meantime, don't hesitate to reach out. We're here to help!
      </p>

      <p class="text-block">
        Looking forward to partnering with you!<br>
        <strong>The AI Talk Coach Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Questions? Email us at partners@aitalkcoach.com</p>
      <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 16px;">
        AI Talk Coach | Partner Program
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
